        "important" : true,
        "name" : "File name",
        "description" : "This expression is used to generate the file names. You have all metadata available as variables. By default, it will summarize all variables (annotations) into a long string. If you do not want to customize the file name, you can create you own string based on available annotations. For example, you can insert <code>#Dataset + \"_\" + Threshold</code> to store the data set and a threshold annotation.\n\nYou can use the following function to automatically generate the name from annotations: <code>SUMMARIZE_ANNOTATIONS_MAP(annotations, \"#\")</code>"
